author: Gamers Nexus
description:
Yes. I hate question marks in titles.

This deep and insightful investigation unveils years of evidence relating to "AI" and its alleged buzzword status. Like this video for the eventual 10-hour version. 

This video is going to be absolutely awful for channel metrics and health, so you should set it to 0.5x and walk away for 20 minutes. But we finally get to comment on AI.
